    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The process of making works primarily of feathers; usually feathers are either adhered to a solid support or tied individually to a woven support.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
